    ComboChart
    A chart that lets you render each series as a different marker type from the following list: columns, lines, and area lines.

    To assign a default marker type for series, use ComboChartOptions.setSeriesType(com.googlecode.gwt.charts.client.options.SeriesType).
    Use the ComboChartOptions.setSeries(int, ComboChartSeries) to specify properties of each series individually.
    ComboChartOptions
    Configuration options for ComboChart.

    Describes the format of a series in the chart.
